title: communication tech for voters
pid: 53ccfd23-a434-44b6-8610-166116b22214
body: |2-
  Building on Rodolfo's WhatsApp group idea, I can imagine that we need to set up the right discourse environment for participants. Even if there were an established collection of personality cults for other candidates, a collection of WhatsApp group structures that made people think with {honesty? courage? peer pressure to be {ethical? kind}} about political ideas (rather than people) might be more powerful.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
